# .env holds ONLY publishable VITE_* client keys (Supabase anon, WalletConnect
# project id) — these ship in the browser bundle by design, so it is committed so
# CI builds are self-contained. Real secrets live in Supabase/Cloudflare env,
# never in the repo. .env.development (Stripe TEST key) stays ignored.
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.development.example

